aratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 12, "EnglishDescription": "If a person touches a number of corpses, or if a person touches one corpse a number of times, then performing one ghusl is sufficient.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar koi shakhs kahi mayyato’n ko mas (touch) kare ya ek mayyit ko kahi martaba mas (touch) kare to ek ghusl kaafi hai.", "UrduDescription": "اگر کوئی شخص کئی میتوں کو مس کرے یا ایک میت کو کئی بار مس کرے تو ایک غسل کافی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1009635, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 13, "EnglishDescription": "There is no problem for someone who has touched a corpse but has not performed the ghusl for touching a corpse to stay in a mosque, or to have sexual intercourse with his wife, or to recite verses of the Qur’an that contain an obligatory sajdah. However, for prayers and suchlike, he must perform ghusl.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jis shakhs ne mayyit ko mas (touch) karne ke baad ghusl na kiya ho uske liye masjid mein thairna (rukna) aur biwi se jimaa (sex) karna aur un aayaat ka padhna jin mein sajdah waajib hai mamnoo (mana) nahi hai, lekin namaz aur us jaisi ibaadat ke liye ghusl karna zaroori hai.", "UrduDescription": "جس شخص نے میت کو مس کرنے کے بعد غسل نہ کیا ہو اس کے لئے مسجد میں ٹھہرنا اور بیوی سے جماع کرنا اور ان آیات کا پڑھنا جن میں سجدہ واجب ہے ممنوع نہیں ہے لیکن نماز اور اس جیسی عبادت کے لئے غسل کرنا ضروری ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2